HEADWORD: Camisole
<hw>Cam"i*sole</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[F. See
<er>chemise</er>.]</ety> <sn>1.</sn> <def>A short dressing jacket for
women.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>A kind of straitjacket.</def>⟦br⟧
